description:
One of the eldest girls under Willem`s care.
Just recently confirmed to be compatible with "dug weapon", the current wielder of Insania, one of the special greatswords used by Heroes of the past. The name of the sword is now also a part of her own name.
Quiet girl, usually wearing a poker face. Loves reading books in her free time. Just like Chtholly sees Willem as someone mysterious.
name: Nephren Ruq Insania
